**User Management**

The **User Management** page allows each organization to add employees or administrators as users within their account.![][image1]

To add a new user:

1. Click the **"Add User"** button located at the top right corner of the page.

2. Fill in the required user details in the pop-up form.

3. Click **"Send Invitation"**.

An invitation email will be sent directly to the user, inviting them to join **VoxDash** under your organization.![][image2]

Once the user accepts the invitation, your organization's name will appear in the header when they log in, indicating they are now part of your team.

Adding users simplifies the process of managing access to projects. Instead of manually configuring permissions, you can simply select the appropriate user when assigning access to a project.
